	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64485469"><p>Plastic is truly unrivaled as a packaging material: it's very light and durable but not extremely strong like, say e.g. steel, it has an almost infinite lifespan (relative to what is wrapped in it), it's easy to produce, it can be transparent (that's important for some stuff).

</p><p>If we try to replace it, we'll have to 1) change people's habits 2) probably make things more expensive and that's not going to be welcomed.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64485469">
